                <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Sulpicius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ani</abbr><ex>ensi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cremo</abbr><ex>na</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XL <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXI <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>testamento fieri <lb n="7"/>iussit arbitratu <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Lucili <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Pub</abbr><ex>lilia</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>heredis
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Schrift in Z. 6-9 zur Kursive neigend. Buchstabenhöhe von oben nach unten abnehmend. Zeile 2 (Ende): O klein. In Bogennische oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes männliche Büste. Auf dem Sockel galoppierender Reiter mit Schild und Lanze.</p>
            </div>
